title: shap.KernelExplainer seems that it cannot correctly identify the data format
body:
I use **pd.read_csv()** to read my data X_train for AutoGluon, and run```explainer = shap.KernelExplainer(predictor.predict_proba, X_train, link="logit")```, but it indicates that there is an error and displays as follows:

```

      2 shap_values = explainer.shap_values(X_test, nsamples=100)
```
